        ---Simple Macro Predicated Language---
                For the developement of x86 assembly programs.

TEST ONE:
        \
                ; BNF
                WSP     = SP | NL | HTAB
                program = *(byte | WSP)
                byte    = '$' *HEXDIG
        \

        $B8 $48 $0E
        $CD $10
        $40
        $CD $10
        $EB $FE

TEST TWO:

        @movax[$B8]
        @int[$CD]
        @incax[$40]
        @jmpshort[$EB]

        movax           $0E48
        int             $10
        incax
        int             $10
        jmpshort        $FE
